main event: A civilian aircraft flying over Memphis, Tennessee reported sighting an unidentified object.
interesting points: The object was observed by the crew of American Airlines flight 243.
The object was reported to be of unknown type, size, and speed.
The object was observed visually from the aircraft.
The object's course was reported as northeast.
The sighting occurred at 23:17 on an unspecified date.
witnesses: Civilian crew of American Airlines flight 243
